AT.name: Eba & Egg: A Hatch Trip
AT.description: In Eba & Egg: A Hatch Trip, control the two main characters simultaneously! Have the two characters split up onto multiple paths and try and find the best path to get a perfect score! Traverse challenging levels to hatch Eba's baby brother or sister! Eba & Egg: A Hatch Trip. Challenge your mind to control two characters at once through a variety of hazards! Over 25 levels! Multiple challenging paths per level! Beat your high score to obtain a better rank! Fast-paced challenging gameplay!
